What you need to know:

But with Nyayo National Stadium out of bound for the league matches, and FKF having failed to secure Moi International Sports Centre Kasarani (main stadium) and Annex Stadium, the issue of lack of venues has again come to the fore.By the time the match between Mathare United and Vihiga United came to an end at Ruaraka on Sunday, it was clear that the ground will be in a very bad shape should it continue hosting more league matches.